---
<Layout>
  <div class="rsa-topbar">🏆 KUZOG FRANCE, lauréate · <strong>Rotary Startup Award 2026</strong> · Rotary Club de Paris &amp; Berlin</div>
  <div class="rsa-nav-rule"></div>

  <header class="rsa-header">
    <nav class="rsa-nav">
      <a class="rsa-brand" href="/">
        <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Rotary" />
        <div class="rsa-brand-sep"></div>
        <div class="rsa-brand-name">
          Rotary Startup Award<span>Paris · Berlin · 2026</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <div class="rsa-nav-right">
        <a
          class="rsa-nav-link"
          href="https://app.rotary-startup.org/Login"
          data-en="Sign in"
          data-de="Anmelden"
        >
          <span class="rsa-nav-link-label">Se connecter</span>
          <span class="rsa-nav-link-arr" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="rsa-hero">
    <div class="rsa-hero-l">
      <div>
        <div class="rsa-hero-meta">
          <span class="rsa-hero-meta-dot"></span>
          <span>Grande Finale — 26 mai 2026</span>
          <span class="rsa-hero-meta-dot"></span>
          <span>Cyrus Conseil, Paris</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="rsa-h1">
          Palmarès<br />
          <strong>Rotary</strong>
          <em>Startup Award</em>
        </h1>
        <div class="rsa-rule"></div>
        <p class="rsa-hero-body">
          Le 26 mai 2026, chez Cyrus Conseil à Paris, cinq startups finalistes
          ont pitché devant un jury de <strong>12 membres</strong>.
          <strong>KUZOG FRANCE</strong> remporte la première édition.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="rsa-hero-bottom">
          <a href="#palmares" class="rsa-btn">Voir le palmarès ↓</a>
        </div>
        <p class="rsa-deadline">
          La Commission Rotary Startup Award — Rotary Club de Paris
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rsa-hero-r">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1475721027785-f74eccf877e2?w=900&auto=format&fit=crop&q=70"
        alt="Grande Finale RSA 2026"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <div class="rsa-hero-badge">
        <div class="rsa-hb-amount">🏆 1er</div>
        <div class="rsa-hb-label">KUZOG FRANCE</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rsa-hero-caption">
        <div class="rsa-hc-l">
          Cyrus Conseil<br />
          Paris, France
        </div>
        <div class="rsa-hc-r">
          Grande Finale<br />
          26 mai 2026
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="rsa-strip">
    <div class="rsa-strip-inner">
      <div class="rsa-si">
        <div class="rsa-si-n">Startups</div>
        <div class="rsa-si-val">27</div>
        <div class="rsa-si-sub">édition 2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rsa-si">
        <div class="rsa-si-n">Finalistes</div>
        <div class="rsa-si-val">5</div>
        <div class="rsa-si-sub">Grande Finale</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rsa-si">
        <div class="rsa-si-n">Jurés finale</div>
        <div class="rsa-si-val">12</div>
